🔍 How Levels Are Determined
The highest level where ALL rules pass becomes your scorecard level. For example:

CodeQuality (Bronze Level)
✅ Bronze rules: All 7 passed (coverage ≥60%, vulnerabilities ≤10, etc.)
❌ Silver rules: 2 failed (code smells = 57, needs ≤50)
❌ Gold rules: 2 failed (code smells = 57, needs ≤10)
Result: Stuck at Bronze until you reduce code smells from 57 to ≤50

DORA Metrics (Elite Level) 🎉
✅ All rules passed at every level
Deployment frequency: 15/week (needs ≥7)
Lead time: 0.8 hours (needs <24)
MTTR: 3 hours (needs <4)
Change failure rate: 0% (needs ≤5%)
